* // ---------- Indexing ---------- // *

# Get information on a query
`db.<collection>.find({<object>}).explain("executionStats")`

# Create an index
`db.<collection>.createIndex({<key and index type specification>:<options})`
// Do not use quotes for the key and index type specification

# Create compound index example
`db.tours.createIndex({tourPrice:1, tourLength:1})`